    <title>New Year Honours for Service personnel and Defence civilians</title>
    <category>News article</category>
    <summary>120 UK Service personnel have been granted state honours by Her Majesty The Queen in the annual New Year Honours list.</summary>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;42 civilians have also been honoured either for work in the Ministry of Defence or in other aspects of UK Defence. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The 162 Defence personnel named in the New Year Honours list for 2013 are as follows:&lt;/p&gt;

